body.p: The following Scandinavians or sold real estate in Chicago recently:
Sven A. Ohlson to Axel Carlson, Avenue J. and 98th Street. Price, $2,400.
104th Place and Wentworth Avenue, A. J. Jacobsen to C. Wohl, $1,000.
Hoyne Avenue at Iowa Street, L. B. Johnson to W. L. Heldt, $5,250.
Robey Street at Clyborn Avenue, Iver Johnson to M. Sloma, $12,630.
Adams street at Francisco Avenue, Catherine Beight to A. M. Michaelson, $3,600.
Kedzie Avenue at Thomas Street, Viking Johnson to C. A. Nardstrom and Theodor Wadstrom, $1,300.
Willow Street at Greenwood Terrace, K. Anderson to Knut O. Burog, $1,100.
Eastwood Avenue at Leavitt Street, V. P. Urgman to Emma Josephine Jenson, $6,000.
Lincoln Avenue at Leland Avenue, F. Seeling to Chas. A. Larsen, 1,400.
Wellington Avenue at Evanston [now Broadway] Avenue, C. A. Nelson to H. Pettilan, $10,750.
